824
00:27:08,866 --> 00:27:09,935
So I introduced the song,

825
00:27:09,936 --> 00:27:12,606
"Here's 'The First Snow Is Falling' by Lee Jung Suk."

826
00:27:12,776 --> 00:27:13,776
"All right."

827
00:27:14,106 --> 00:27:17,246
The first snow is falling

828
00:27:17,946 --> 00:27:19,646
So that I wouldn't make fun of him.

829
00:27:20,816 --> 00:27:22,015
(Singing while walking on eggshells)

830
00:27:22,016 --> 00:27:24,315
- Wait.
- For real. I'm not exaggerating.

831
00:27:24,316 --> 00:27:25,915
My senior during military service did the same thing.

832
00:27:25,916 --> 00:27:26,955
Really?

833
00:27:26,956 --> 00:27:28,085
