927
00:30:29,666 --> 00:30:32,135
"What? You're just like me."

928
00:30:32,136 --> 00:30:33,645
Even your voice is the same.

929
00:30:33,646 --> 00:30:35,246
"I'm Bin."

930
00:30:35,476 --> 00:30:37,845
- Gosh, look at that.
- You do look like him.

931
00:30:37,846 --> 00:30:39,475
I'm doing this so I don't get scolded.

932
00:30:39,476 --> 00:30:41,745
- I was so scared.
- No way.

933
00:30:41,746 --> 00:30:43,185
- BewhY.
- A distorted BewhY.

934
00:30:43,186 --> 00:30:44,985
Yes, I do look like BewhY.

935
00:30:44,986 --> 00:30:46,385
- You should rap.
- Yes.

936
00:30:46,386 --> 00:30:48,085
- A distorted BewhY.
- "We recognize the authentic."

937
00:30:48,086 --> 00:30:49,385
That's so similar.

938
00:30:49,386 --> 00:30:50,395
Even his mouth.

939
00:30:50,396 --> 00:30:51,625
- He's the same.
- That's right.

940
00:30:51,626 --> 00:30:52,855
You have three cats now, right?

941
00:30:52,856 --> 00:30:53,865
- I have three.
- That's his background.

942
00:30:53,866 --> 00:30:54,866
Let's see your cats.

943
00:30:54,866 --> 00:30:55,866
Let's see.

944
00:30:55,867 --> 00:30:57,235
They are so popular.

945
00:30:57,236 --> 00:30:58,295
They are so cute.

946
00:30:58,296 --> 00:30:59,365
- Come on.
- Seriously.

947
00:30:59,366 --> 00:31:00,735
You had two cats,

948
00:31:00,736 --> 00:31:02,105
but there's a new one, right?

949
00:31:02,106 --> 00:31:03,735
Yes, we recently adopted another one.

950
00:31:03,736 --> 00:31:05,275
Tell us about each one of them.

951
00:31:05,276 --> 00:31:06,505
To explain,

952
00:31:06,506 --> 00:31:08,806
the first one is Chunbong.

953
00:31:09,076 --> 00:31:10,845
He has the most views.

954
00:31:10,846 --> 00:31:13,245
If we put Chunbong's face up, we get a million views.

955
00:31:13,246 --> 00:31:15,345
- That's a dutiful cat.
